commit.message:
sseregparm-1.c, [...]: Run only on 32-bit x86.

	* gcc.target/i386/sseregparm-1.c, gcc.target/i386/sseregparm-2.c,
	gcc.target/i386/fastcall-sseregparm.c,
	gcc.target/i386/regparm-stdcall.c: Run only on 32-bit x86.

From-SVN: r101202

+	gcc.target/i386/fastcall-sseregparm.c,
